{
  "stem": "21786.8",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I have got the route.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We did it, I mean, I did it in 1995.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Last year we-- I retraced it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It was 350 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From 18 of April to the 1 of May.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We came to a city called Varnsdorf, which was already on the Czech territory, former Czech territory.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was Sudetenland.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was part of Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then they let us stay in a evacuated textile factory.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When the SS found out that Hitler committed suicide, and-- that still didn't stop them to hang people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And whoever, I mean, we were suspected that they wanted to escape.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they split us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They took about 250 Aryans who were in the camp, they took them away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this had-- the German head, Kapelke, persuaded them that-- listen now the logic what they used.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you leave the prisoners, or if you shoot them, so what will happen?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most probably the war is lost, though the SS men protested.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We have got a secret weapon.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Fuhrer-- he says, there is no Fuhrer.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't depend on secret weapon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you kill the Jews, you will be killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] On the other hand, you need the Jews, for if you don't have the Jews, you have to go and fight the Russians.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You still are trained soldiers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You've got the weapon and ammunition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Put the Jews on the train and let them take them to the nearest camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Don't try to kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They followed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They put us on wagons, flat coal wagons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There were not so many.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, there might have been 40, 50 in one wagon.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
